Setting World Records in MINECRAFT! ►► http://bit.ly/1OTRYlb
Would You Rather - StankPat Begins! ►► http://bit.ly/1Y30Gjt

I'm really having a great time getting to know YOU all while playing games like "Would You Rather..." To continue the leaning experience, I'm going to play a similar game that many of you have been asking me to play - "Will You Press The Button?" Let's see what deep thought provoking questions this game has in store for me today.

Follow all the updates on new episodes of GTLive!
